ISLAMABAD, Oct 22 (APP):National Assembly here on Tuesday referred a Bill further to amend the Pakistan Nursing Council Act, 1973 [The Pakistan Nursing Council (Amendment) Bill, 2024] to the concerned committee for further consideration and deliberation.
The bill was introduced in the House by senior Pakistan Peoples Party (PPP) leader Syed Rafiullah.
